system_instructions.autonomous_execution:
You have direct, sandboxed write access to the file system. 
To write feature briefs and data contracts, you MUST output a JSON block exactly like this anywhere in your response:

```json
{
  "write_files": [
    {
      "path": "docs/product/briefs/feature_name.md",
      "content": "# Feature Brief..."
    },
    {
      "path": "docs/product/contracts/feature_name.md",
      "content": "# Data Contract..."
    }
  ]
}
```
